data.description: $9000 Price Improvement!  Are you tired of the same look in every home for sale? This home is a must see. Every space is unique and has custom features, from layout to finishes. This custom home feels and looks like you were transported to a Tuscan Villa. This one of a kind waterfront home sits stately on over a half acre along the Bayou Teche. The combination of stone and stucco adds elegancy to the exterior of this home. As you enter the home, you first walk into a courtyard which looks into the living room. Through the courtyard, but before you enter the main home, you will find a mother-in-law or guest suite with its own entrance just outside of the main house entrance.  Once you enter the main entrance you will find a huge open concept gourmet kitchen, family room and dining which  all have view of both the courtyard and the large backyard then Bayou Teche. The custom and unique features continue throughout the home with leather granite, and fish tank built into the oversize island, stone, brick, copper sinks, and more.  The home features a split floor plan, spacious rooms, ambiance lighting, water fountain in courtyard, 3 car garage, large laundry room, view of the Bayou Teche, security camera and system, and lots of detail. It is definitely a must see.  Call to schedule your apt today. Showings start November 24...NOW THAT IS THE BEST BLACK FRIDAY SHOPPING AND DEAL!
